data.description: Welcome to your oasis in Miramar, Florida! This fully updated, move-in-ready single-family home boasts the convenience of one-story living with three spacious bedrooms and two luxurious baths, offering both comfort and style. Entertain effortlessly in the backyard retreat, complete with a sparkling pool, perfect for those sunny Florida days. Nestled in a sought-after neighborhood, this property combines modern amenities with the charm of suburban living, promising a serene escape while still being close to city conveniences. Don't miss the opportunity to make this your dream home!
